Increased demand for electric transport, smart grids and PV will put
increased pressure on the network.

UtilityWeek has brought together16 expertsto address the challenges and
opportunities facing the energy sector as it transitions to a low-carbon and
more energy efficient environment.

Organisations sharing their research, strategies and case studies
at the 2015�Demand�Response�Future Networks�Conference, taking place on�March
